            <span class="tag tag-news">News</span>
            <h3>PAGCOR-Licensed Sportsbooks Brace for a World Cup Betting Surge</h3>
            <p class="card-dek">The expanded 48-team FIFA World Cup kicks off June 11 — the largest sports-betting event the licensed PIGO market has faced since the August 2025 delinking reset. It arrives months after PAGCOR cut the live sports betting GGR share rate to 15%, and the question is how much of the surge the regulated market can capture.</p>
            <p class="card-meta">June 2, 2026 &middot; Score 9/10</p>
          </div>
        </a>

